test_all_minus_one_range:
assert <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x75d0d042f1f0> == -((86 - 43) + 1)
 +  where <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x75d0d042f1f0> = sum_odd_ints_inclusive([-1, -1, -1, -1, -1, -1, ...])
test_negative_odd_range:
assert <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x7390a5bd31f0> == (-9 * ((86 - 43) + 1))
 +  where <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x7390a5bd31f0> = sum_odd_ints_inclusive([-9, -9, -9, -9, -9, -9, ...])
test_all_zero_range:
assert <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x7e11f3f9b1f0> == 0
 +  where <generator object sum_odd_ints_inclusive at 0x7e11f3f9b1f0> = sum_odd_ints_inclusive([0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...])
